{"tha-ap379:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap379:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap379:0.3":"Citakapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap379:1.1":"“Parinibbute bhagavati, ","tha-ap379:1.2":"jalajuttamanamake; ","tha-ap379:1.3":"Aropitamhi citake, ","tha-ap379:1.4":"salapupphamapujayim. ","tha-ap379:2.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap379:2.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap379:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap379:2.4":"citapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap379:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap379:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap379:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap379:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap379:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap379:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap379:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap379:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap379:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap379:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma citakapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap379:7.1":"Citakapujakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}